Marathon Structured Product Strategies Fund, LP: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 22, 2017 3:27 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Marathon Structured Product Strategies Fund, LP



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Marathon Structured Product Strategies Fund, LP is a hedge fund launched and managed by Marathon Asset Management, LP. The fund invests in fixed income markets. Marathon Structured Product Strategies Fund, LP was formed in August 2014 and is domiciled in United States.


One Bryant Park38th floorNew York, NY 10036United StatesFounded in 2014



Phone: 212-500-3000

Fax: 212-205-8800








Key Executives for Marathon Structured Product Strategies Fund, LP




Mr. Bruce Jeffrey Richards


      	Portfolio Manager
      


Age: 56
        




Compensation as of Fiscal Year 2017. 



